@startuml sequenceDiagram
'на основі UC1 (перегляд рекомендацій)
actor Користувач
participant "UI" as UI
participant "RecommendationService" as Service
participant "RecommendationEngine" as Engine
participant "ReviewRepository" as Repo

Користувач -> UI: Запит рекомендацій
UI -> Service: getPersonalRecommendations(userId)
Service -> Engine: generateRecommendations(user)
Engine -> Repo: getUserReviewsAndPreferences(userId)
Repo --> Engine: reviews + preferences
Engine -> Engine: analyzePreferences()
Engine -> Repo: getTopRatedDishesByCuisine()
Repo --> Engine: dishes
Engine -> Engine: calculateScores()
Engine --> Service: List<RecommendationDTO> + explanations
Service --> UI: Показати рекомендації
UI --> Користувач: Відобразити список
@enduml